room_title: Escape room "Project Capricorn" by The Puzzle Masters Escape Rooms in Tacoma
room_description:
WANTED: Somebody to go back in time for us. Safety not guaranteed.

Hey, my name is David! The Zodiac murders are some of the worst unsolved crimes in history. Thankfully, my team and I have created the technology to go back in time and correct the injustices of the past.

Not-so-thankfully, this technology is also mostly untested and extremely dangerous, so our newly-minted Project Capricorn isn't exactly getting a lot of excited volunteers. 

Man, we desperately need volunteers.

We lost the last batch in a time vortex. The mess was indescribable. We were scrubbing down the walls for days.

Anyway, can you and your friends help us out?
